{"tid":2458494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解藍絲家人都比人拉","createTime":"2021-03-23T12:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T14:26:04.000Z","uid":35054,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f243ae8e5202dd9a4c5f9eab409f715ef99d6ad0","tid":2458494,"uid":35054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T12:40:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210323/DOKZGZR76VFJ5AFZJW5YR644NA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210323%2FDOKZGZR76VFJ5AFZJW5YR644NA%2F&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97SK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=b39a96e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210323%2FDOKZGZR76VFJ5AFZJW5YR644NA%2F&h=980ad11e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210323/DOKZGZR76VFJ5AFZJW5YR644NA/</a><br />\n<br />\n海關早前於一個由加拿大空運到港的郵包內發現大麻花，其後根據收貨地，今午掩至西貢南圍村進行掃毒，並在一村屋內拘捕一名54歲女子，據知該人為<span class=\"red\"><strong>吳耀漢的女兒</strong></span>。海關又在單位內發現13棵大麻植物，及一批含大麻成份的朱古力，估計上址被人用作大麻種植場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔通佢個女係黃嘅？<br />\nbetween 聽講大麻喺連登係都好大爭議"},{"pid":"ff264ed1b6c418794300f62d456a6e944057745f","tid":2458494,"uid":103230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T12:41:32.000Z","msg":"吳耀漢又搞搞震<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022f46367be4f16c47a1ab497abbc95110dde62c","tid":2458494,"uid":140523,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T12:51:37.000Z","msg":"你點影的？"},{"pid":"9a3ffa35d853ef58386f536d4be8171d89e78487","tid":2458494,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T13:01:31.000Z","msg":"54歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />撈咗幾耐"},{"pid":"e54bbab6460c4d16de734e4e5a0f54f8fd311e94","tid":2458494,"uid":12831,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T13:02:43.000Z","msg":"咪撚上腦啦 拉9毒犯理得你黃定藍<img src=\"/a